metadata.name: Party Crasher (Target)
metadata.description:
First purchaser of this NFT receives the physical hand finished stereo-lithograph in glass cloche based on the NFT 3D animation created by Jason Freeny. Proof and verification of NFT purchase will be required. Allow 30 days for delivery after verification.

Physical piece can be seen here- [Party Crasher A metafetus IG](https://www.instagram.com/p/CXgeJh1upWF/).

Making of can be seen here- [Party Crasher B metafetus IG](https://www.instagram.com/p/CXlikDilTXC/).
